{
  "doc_id": "31127",
  "text": "The entire iTRAQ dataset, regardless of protein ratio, was uploaded into Cytoscape v3.3.0 [CITATION_1] and analyzed using the ReactomeFI plugin (database 2015) [CITATION_2] to generate an interactome, followed by a pathway enrichment analysis. Gene ontology enrichment analysis for biological process, cellular component, and molecular function were completed using the cytoscape app BiNGO [CITATION_3] and REVIGO [CITATION_4] . The iTRAQ ratio (expression) data was overlaid with biological annotations to prioritize proteins for SRM analysis.",
